===Etymology===
From the English {{term|inflexion|lang=en}}, from the {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|inflexio|lang=la}}, {{term|inflexionis||a bending away from|lang=la}}; the spelling ''inflection'' is due to influence from {{term|correction}}.

