===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}

# {{context|grammar|lang=en}} A change in the form of a word that reflects a change in grammatical function.
#: ''an '''inflection''' for gender, number, or tense''
# A change in [[pitch]] or [[tone]] of voice.
# {{context|mathematics|lang=en}} A change in curvature from [[concave]] to [[convex]] or from convex to concave.
# A turning away from a straight course.
# {{context|optometry|lang=en}} [[diffraction]]

